  <brief_title>A Study of Controlled-Release Carvedilol Compared to Immediate-Release Carvedilol in Patients With Primary Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II, Multi-center, Multiple-dose, Double-blind, Randomized, Crossover Study Comparing the Pharmacodynamic Effects of a Once-daily Controlled-Release Carvedilol (CRC; Egalet® Formulation) and an Immediate-Release Carvedilol (IRC) Formulation in Patients With Primary Hypertension</official_title>
